        "timestamp": "2019-10-09 12:23:13.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHi,\n\nI have now made changes for AAI-2676 to remove the search guard from the setup-in master branch. This fix is basically a port of https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/aai/search-data-service/+/96354 to master branch.\n\nThis has been tested by in my local lab (note that in my lab- due to test certificate issue, I had to use old pom.xml to build my search data image to do end to end testing but all code base was from master branch only , hence I presume it should be fine).\n\nFyi, test steps done by me via postman to search data MS:\n1. Create a new index.\n2. Add new document.\n3. Query the document.\nExpect successful responses.\n\n\nI would be thankful to you if you could please review and approve.\n\nRegards,\nRajeev",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
